race.comment: ROYAL ZULU (3) goes very well at the course and distance with two wins and a placing from four starts. In the money last time at this track (24.02) in a Grade 5, finishing a nose second. Has the ability and should feature. CANE SMOKE (1) flew the lids from out wide with an impressive turn of foot, going on to clock 23.89 when a 4.5 lengths winner over 407m at this track last time. Winner at his latest appearance in one of the quickest times on the card. Significant danger. NOVELIST (2) is a talented type and proved too classy last time to win by a nose at this track in a handy 24.03 beating EXPLOITATION. Likely to be in the finish. KOOLBOO KID (7) has ability and can find the frame.
